## Integration Opportunities

### With PAI
- Judge skill aligns with PAI's JudgeGate workflow
- Different failure mode taxonomy could complement
- Team-skills uses `telemetry-*` prefix, PAI uses TitleCase

### With SystemMap
- ADR skill useful for documenting cross-system decisions
- Mermaid skill useful for architecture diagrams in ai.md files

---

## Working Here

### Quick Start
```bash
git clone git@github.com:BonkBotTeam/team-skills.git
cd team-skills
make install
```

### Common Locations
| Task | Path |
|------|------|
| Add skill | `skills/telemetry-<name>/SKILL.md` |
| Modify install | `scripts/install.sh` |
| Track progress | `PROGRESS.md` |

